---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <Head Title='Le Blond'/>
</head>
<Gtag/>
<body class="bg-white dark:bg-black box-border overflow-x-clip">
    <Navbar />
    <Menu />
    <!--Project-->
    <Image src={cover} alt="" class="h-lvh w-full object-cover" />
    <div class="grid-cols-scale gap-x-5 p-3 pb-20 pt-9 md:px-8 md:pt-10">
          <ProjectHeader 
            Title='LE BLOND'
            Visible1=`` Info1=`Branding`
            Visible2=`` Info2='Illustrator, Photoshop, After Effects, Figma'
            Visible3=`hidden` Info3=''
            Visible4=`hidden` Info4=' '
            Body=`Le Blond is an outdoor apparel brand and retail store based in Spokane, Washington, targeting women ages 45-65 who embrace outdoor living. Inspired by the resilience of historical outdoor women like Elizabeth le Blond, the brand values dependability, authenticity, legacy, and community. It makes clothing designed to empower women to perform their best in the outdoors, embodying confidence and resilience. It’s apparel that understands you—gear you can trust, no matter where the journey leads.`
            />
          <Image src={img1} alt="" class="img-full reveal lg:mt-32" />
          <Image src={img2} alt="" class="img-full mb-0 reveal" />
          <div class="block-full my-20 md:my-[175px] reveal">
            <div class="title text-black dark:text-white font-sans font-regular tracking-widest pb-10 md:pb-[50px] ">WHAT IS THE BRAND?</div>
            <div class="body-copy font-mono pb-3 md:pb-[24px]">Le Blond positions itself as...</div>
            <div class="text-hmd text-black dark:text-white font-sans font-extralight tracking-wide md:text-hlg lg:text-dsm lg:leading-tight">The outdoor brand making apparel that reflects the strength, wit, reliability, and legacy of the women who wear it.</div>
          </div>
          <Image src={img4} alt="" class="img-full reveal" />
          <video class="img-full reveal" autoplay="" loop="" muted playsinline="" data-object-fit="cover">
            <source src="/project-leBlond/36_1.mp4" type="video/mp4"/>
          </video>
          <div class="block-full m-0 md:my-[175px] md:flex md:flex-row items-center gap-[3.255vw] lg:mx-[5.199vw] reveal">
            <Image src={img5} alt="" class="img-full w-[506.277px] reveal"/>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 lg:gap-[40px]">
              <div class="title text-black dark:text-white font-sans font-regular tracking-widest">WHO IS THIS FOR?</div>
              <div class="headline text-black dark:text-white font-sans font-extralight tracking-wide lg:leading-tight">Ladies who live outdoors.</div>
              <div class="body-copy">For women, ages 45-65 who are active all year.  they hike, bike, ski, camp, kayak, and swim with their friends. They care about performance and reliability over style. They trust brands that know them and have a reputation.  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <Image src={img15} alt="" class="img-full reveal" />
          <div class="block-full my-5 md:my-[175px] md:flex md:flex-row items-center md:justify-between gap-7 lg:mx-[8.104vw] reveal">
            <Image src={img7} alt="" class="img-full mb-5 md:m-0 min-w-10 max-w-[426.197px] reveal" />
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:justify-between h-full max-w-[600px]">
              <div class="text-tlg text-black dark:text-white font-sans font-light tracking-widest">Elizabeth Le Blond</div>
              <div class="body-copy">Elizabeth le Blond was a pioneering female mountaineer in the late 19th century. In 1907, she founded the Ladies’ Alpine Club, creating a space for women passionate about climbing. Despite societal expectations, she and her fellow mountaineers achieved extraordinary feats—all while wearing dresses. Their clothing constantly worked against them, making already formidable climbs even more challenging.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <Image src={img8} alt="" class="img-full reveal" />
          <div class="block-full flex flex-col gap-7 mb-10 md:my-[175px] md:flex-row justify-between lg:mx-[3.827vw] reveal">
            <div class="text-hsm text-black dark:text-white font-sans font-light tracking-widest ">But these women didn’t let those limitations define them. They adapted, persevered, and excelled, proving that determination can overcome constraints.</div>
            <div class="body-copy">This brand takes Inspiration from women like Le Blond. It seeks to create apparel that reflects their strength, wit, reliability, and legacy. No matter the challenge, they found a way to make it work. We make clothing that embodies this attitude. Clothing that is designed to enable women to preform their best in the outdoors. Apparel that gets you. Apparel you can trust.</div>
          </div>
          <video class="img-full reveal" autoplay="" loop="" muted playsinline="" data-object-fit="cover">
            <source src="/project-leBlond/33_1.mp4" type="video/mp4"/>
          </video>
          <Image src={img14} alt="" class="img-full reveal" />
          <Image src={img16} alt="" class="img-full reveal" />
          <Image src={img17} alt="" class="img-left reveal" />
          <Image src={img19} alt="" class="img-right reveal" />
          <Image src={img20} alt="" class="img-full reveal" />
          <video class="img-full reveal" autoplay="" loop="" muted playsinline="" data-object-fit="cover">
            <source src="/project-leBlond/34_1.mp4" type="video/mp4"/>
          </video>
